{
  "text": "The composite resins emergence has provided higher aesthetic quality in dental restorations. However, the mechanical properties of the resins, especially the high levels of shrinkage stress caused by volumetric variations during the activation process, are the main problem in the practical application of these materials [CITATION_1] 5 .",
